{
  "vision": {
    "en": "The SCCD Alumni Association connects generations of communications design graduates, fostering lifelong learning, mentorship, and professional collaboration. Through events, mentorship programs, and industry partnerships, we sustain a vibrant community that bridges academia and practice. Our mission is to amplify the impact of SCCD alumni across the global design landscape, support emerging talents, and give back to the next generation of designers.",
    "zh": "實踐大學媒體傳達設計學系系友會凝聚歷屆畢業學長姊，建立終身學習、相互提攜與專業合作的網絡。透過活動、職涯導師制度、產業合作，我們延續學系精神，搭建學界與業界的橋樑。我們的使命是擴大 SCCD 系友在全球設計版圖上的影響力，扶持新銳人才，回饋下一代設計師。"
  },
